quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  3,113,"Boosi shibali nashilala tawe, khulimwo nende Abandu beshitabu baandi beema obulayi basomanga tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye eshilo nende eshitere nabo khandi bamwinamilanga (nibasujuda)"
  3,114,"Basuubilanga Nyasaye nende Inyanga yeyindukho, nebalomesinjia okhukhola amalayi, nebakaaninjia amabii, ne belushilanga okhukhola amakhuwa amalayi. Ne abo nibo abali mubakholi abamalayi"
  3,115,"Nekabakhola mumalayi shibaliimwa omurungo kwako tawe, Ne Nyasaye amanyile muno abamuria"
  3,116,"Toto balia abakhaya (abakhayi) , omwandu kwabu nohomba Abana babu shibalibakhoonya shiosishiosi imbeli wa Nyasaye tawe, ne abo nibo Abandu bomumulilo balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi"
  3,117,"Ebia murusinjia khubulamu bwokhushialo buno bili shinga omuyeka kulinende omunyiri khweibarafu, mana nikunyoola omukunda kwa Abandu bakholela obubii emioyo chiabu mana nikunyasia. Ne Nyasaye shabakholelanga obubii tawe halali abeene nibo bekholelanga obubii"
  3,118,"Enywe Abasuubili mulakhola okhuba ebesikwa benyu Abandu balali ninanyu tawe. Shibalalekha okhubakholela obubii tawe. Bayanza okhulola akamunyasia. Imalile okhumanyikha isila yabu khuminwa chiabu, ne kabafisanga mubilifu biabu ni amakhongo muno. Khumalile okhulolosilia ebimanyisio nimuba toto nimuretsanga mubwongo"
  3,119,"Mana enywe bano mwabachama, nabo shibabachama tawe, Nanyu musuubilanga ebitabu biosi. Ne nibabukanana ninanyu nibaboola mbu; “khusuubile “ , ne nibaba bonyene babalumilanga tsinzala khu isila. Boola “fwe nende isila yenyu, toto Nyasaye yamanya kali mubilifu.”"
  3,120,"Ni munyoola obulayi bwosibwosi bibasinyisia, nenimunyoolaobubiibibasangasia. Neni mwisumilisia mana mumurie (Nyasaye), omubayo kwabu shikulabakhola shiosishiosi tawe, Toto Nyasaye abotokhananga koosi kabakholanga"
  3,121,"Ne olwa warula mumabwibwi nolekha Abandu bobo, shichila okhupanga Abasuubili muliyie, ne Nyasaye awuulilanga ne amanyile muno"
  3,122,"Emikanda chibili mwinywe nichinjilamwo oburi, mbu betsa okhushilwa, ne Nyasaye niye omulindi wabu, Ne Abasuubili besikesa Nyasaye yenyene"
  3,123,Ne Nyasaye yabahabina mubadiri nanyu nimuli abateshele. Kho murie Nyasaye kho munyoole okhupa orio
  3,124,Olwa waboolela Abasuubili mbu; ‘’koo shibibayela tawe nikali mbu Nyasaye wenyu alabakhoonya nende Abamalaika elfu tsitaru abeshibwa (okhurula mwikulu)?’’
  3,125,"Koo, nimwista okhuba abesumilisi mana murie Nyasaye nekata Abasuku nibabarusia mapwoka, awo Nyasaye wenyu omulesi alabakhoonya nende Abamalaika elfu tsirano batsunukhanga nibalwana namaani"
  3,126,"Ne Nyasaye shiyakhola kano halali bube obusangali khwinywe, ne emioyo chenyu chinyoole okhwihotselesia, ne obukhoonyi shiburulanga awundi tawe halali khu Nyasaye, Owoluyali Owamani Owamachesi"
  3,127,"Endio nilwokhuba atete ebuleka khubakhayi nohomba abaresie banyoole okhukalukha inyuma, nabo nibatorere"
  3,128,"Na ewe obula liosiliosi mukano, nalabaleshela nohomba abahelesie eshinyasio shichilabo ni abamabii"
  3,129,"Nebiosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo ni bia Nyasaye, aleshelanga wayenya ne ahelesinjia wayenya eshinyasio, ne Nyasaye ni Omulesheli muno Owetsimbabaasi"
  3,130,"Enywe Abasuubila, mulalia riba tawe nimumetelakhwo hekulu hekulu, ne murie Nyasaye khomunyoole okhubura"
  3,131,Ne murie omulilo kwarecheshelwa abakhayi
  3,132,Ne wulile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe kho munyoole tsimbabaasi